  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Professional Polish\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Professional Polish\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] bg-slate-50 font-sans text-slate-900 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- LEFT: BRAIN DUMP CHAT (38%) -->\\n  <div class=\\\"w-[380px] flex flex-col border-r border-slate-200 bg-white\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6 border-bottom border-slate-100\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-800\\\">Last-Minute Life Saver</h1>\\n      </div>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500\\\">Processing frantic inputs in real-time...</p>\\n    </div>\\n    \\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-4 flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"self-end bg-blue-600 text-white p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none max-w-[85%] text-sm shadow-sm\\\">\\n        I have a board presentation at 4 PM, haven\'t finished the financial slides, need to pick up dry cleaning, and my cat has a vet appointment at 2! HELP.\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"self-start bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none max-w-[85%] text-sm border border-slate-200\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"font-semibold block mb-1 text-blue-700\\\">AI Assistant</span>\\n        Calm down. I\'ve mapped this out. I\'m prioritizing the slides now. I\'ve flagged the vet as a high-dependency move. \\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"self-end bg-blue-600 text-white p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none max-w-[85%] text-sm shadow-sm\\\">\\n        Wait, also need to send the pre-read by 1:30 PM. I\'m panicking.\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"self-start bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none max-w-[85%] text-sm border border-slate-200\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"font-semibold block mb-1 text-blue-700\\\">AI Assistant</span>\\n        Added to the matrix. I am shifting your \'Execution Blocks\' to account for the 1:30 deadline. Look at the right panel.\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"p-4 border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n        <textarea \\n          readonly\\n          class=\\\"w-full h-24 p-3 text-sm border border-slate-300 rounded-xl bg-white resize-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none\\\"\\n          placeholder=\\\"Type your frantic thoughts...\\\"\\n        >I also forgot to email Sarah about the budget approval...</textarea>\\n        <button class=\\\"absolute bottom-2 right-2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold\\\">Process Dump</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- RIGHT: DYNAMIC DASHBOARD (62%) -->\\n  <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col p-8 gap-6\\\">\\n    <!-- TOP: TRIAGE MATRIX -->\\n    <div>\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-3\\\">Task Triage Matrix</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4\\\">\\n        <!-- URGENT & CRITICAL -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-red-50 border border-red-100 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold bg-red-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">URGENT</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-red-700 font-medium\\\">2 Items</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-red-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Financial Slides (Draft 2)\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-red-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Board Pre-read Email\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- HIGH DEPENDENCY -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold bg-amber-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">DEPENDENCY</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-amber-700 font-medium\\\">1 Item</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-amber-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Vet Appointment (Cat)\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- MICRO-TASKS -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">MICRO</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-blue-700 font-medium\\\">2 Items</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-blue-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Dry Cleaning Pickup\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-blue-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Sarah: Budget Email\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- BOTTOM: EXECUTION TIMELINE -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-3\\\">Survival Execution Timeline</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 relative\\\">\\n        <!-- Time Grid -->\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute left-6 top-6 bottom-6 w-12 flex flex-col justify-between text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-mono\\\">\\n          <div>12:00</div>\\n          <div>13:00</div>\\n          <div>14:00</div>\\n          <div>15:00</div>\\n          <div>16:00</div>\\n          <div>17:00</div>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"ml-16 h-full border-l border-slate-100 relative\\\">\\n          <!-- Execution Blocks -->\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-0 left-4 right-4 h-[18%] bg-blue-600/10 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-3 rounded-r shadow-sm\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-800\\\">Deep Work: Financial Slide Deck</span>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-blue-600\\\">Focus Mode: Do Not Disturb Enabled</p>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[20%] left-4 right-4 h-[8%] bg-red-600/10 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-3 rounded-r shadow-sm\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-red-800 uppercase\\\">Deadline: Send Pre-read</span>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[32%] left-4 right-4 h-[15%] bg-amber-600/10 border-l-4 border-amber-600 p-3 rounded-r shadow-sm\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-amber-800\\\">Movement: Vet & Cleaning Run</span>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-amber-600\\\">Audio-memo Sarah during transit</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[52%] left-4 right-4 h-[25%] bg-slate-800 border-l-4 border-slate-900 p-3 rounded-r shadow-lg\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-white\\\">BOARD PRESENTATION</span>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400\\\">In-room 402B</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Indicator Line -->\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[12%] left-0 right-0 h-px bg-red-400 z-10 flex items-center\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-400 -ml-1\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"ml-2 text-[9px] font-bold text-red-500 bg-white px-1\\\">CURRENT TIME</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    \\n    <!-- AGENT STATUS BAR -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 text-white p-3 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-1\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-mono opacity-80 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Agent Status: Optimizing Schedule...</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-60 flex gap-4\\\">\\n        <span>call: parse_deadline_urgency</span>\\n        <span>call: schedule_calendar_block</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Professional Polish\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Professional Polish\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] bg-slate-50 font-sans text-slate-900 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- LEFT: BRAIN DUMP CHAT (38%) -->\\n  <div class=\\\"w-[380px] flex flex-col border-r border-slate-200 bg-white\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6 border-bottom border-slate-100\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-800\\\">Last-Minute Life Saver</h1>\\n      </div>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500\\\">Processing frantic inputs in real-time...</p>\\n    </div>\\n    \\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-4 flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"self-end bg-blue-600 text-white p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none max-w-[85%] text-sm shadow-sm\\\">\\n        I have a board presentation at 4 PM, haven\'t finished the financial slides, need to pick up dry cleaning, and my cat has a vet appointment at 2! HELP.\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"self-start bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none max-w-[85%] text-sm border border-slate-200\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"font-semibold block mb-1 text-blue-700\\\">AI Assistant</span>\\n        Calm down. I\'ve mapped this out. I\'m prioritizing the slides now. I\'ve flagged the vet as a high-dependency move. \\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"self-end bg-blue-600 text-white p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none max-w-[85%] text-sm shadow-sm\\\">\\n        Wait, also need to send the pre-read by 1:30 PM. I\'m panicking.\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"self-start bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none max-w-[85%] text-sm border border-slate-200\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"font-semibold block mb-1 text-blue-700\\\">AI Assistant</span>\\n        Added to the matrix. I am shifting your \'Execution Blocks\' to account for the 1:30 deadline. Look at the right panel.\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"p-4 border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n        <textarea \\n          readonly\\n          class=\\\"w-full h-24 p-3 text-sm border border-slate-300 rounded-xl bg-white resize-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none\\\"\\n          placeholder=\\\"Type your frantic thoughts...\\\"\\n        >I also forgot to email Sarah about the budget approval...</textarea>\\n        <button class=\\\"absolute bottom-2 right-2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold\\\">Process Dump</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- RIGHT: DYNAMIC DASHBOARD (62%) -->\\n  <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col p-8 gap-6\\\">\\n    <!-- TOP: TRIAGE MATRIX -->\\n    <div>\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-3\\\">Task Triage Matrix</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4\\\">\\n        <!-- URGENT & CRITICAL -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-red-50 border border-red-100 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold bg-red-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">URGENT</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-red-700 font-medium\\\">2 Items</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-red-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Financial Slides (Draft 2)\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-red-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Board Pre-read Email\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- HIGH DEPENDENCY -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold bg-amber-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">DEPENDENCY</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-amber-700 font-medium\\\">1 Item</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-amber-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Vet Appointment (Cat)\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <!-- MICRO-TASKS -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">MICRO</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-blue-700 font-medium\\\">2 Items</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-blue-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Dry Cleaning Pickup\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-white p-2 rounded border border-blue-200 text-xs shadow-sm\\\">\\n              Sarah: Budget Email\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- BOTTOM: EXECUTION TIMELINE -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-3\\\">Survival Execution Timeline</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 relative\\\">\\n        <!-- Time Grid -->\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute left-6 top-6 bottom-6 w-12 flex flex-col justify-between text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-mono\\\">\\n          <div>12:00</div>\\n          <div>13:00</div>\\n          <div>14:00</div>\\n          <div>15:00</div>\\n          <div>16:00</div>\\n          <div>17:00</div>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"ml-16 h-full border-l border-slate-100 relative\\\">\\n          <!-- Execution Blocks -->\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-0 left-4 right-4 h-[18%] bg-blue-600/10 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-3 rounded-r shadow-sm\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-800\\\">Deep Work: Financial Slide Deck</span>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-blue-600\\\">Focus Mode: Do Not Disturb Enabled</p>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[20%] left-4 right-4 h-[8%] bg-red-600/10 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-3 rounded-r shadow-sm\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-red-800 uppercase\\\">Deadline: Send Pre-read</span>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[32%] left-4 right-4 h-[15%] bg-amber-600/10 border-l-4 border-amber-600 p-3 rounded-r shadow-sm\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-amber-800\\\">Movement: Vet & Cleaning Run</span>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-amber-600\\\">Audio-memo Sarah during transit</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[52%] left-4 right-4 h-[25%] bg-slate-800 border-l-4 border-slate-900 p-3 rounded-r shadow-lg\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-white\\\">BOARD PRESENTATION</span>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400\\\">In-room 402B</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Indicator Line -->\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-[12%] left-0 right-0 h-px bg-red-400 z-10 flex items-center\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-400 -ml-1\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"ml-2 text-[9px] font-bold text-red-500 bg-white px-1\\\">CURRENT TIME</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    \\n    <!-- AGENT STATUS BAR -->\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 text-white p-3 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-1\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-mono opacity-80 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Agent Status: Optimizing Schedule...</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-60 flex gap-4\\\">\\n        <span>call: parse_deadline_urgency</span>\\n        <span>call: schedule_calendar_block</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
